msgstr "Canonical API name: `ptool.re.Regex:find`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:74
msgid "`re:find(input[, init])` returns the first match in `input`, or `nil`."
msgstr "`re:find(input[, init])` は `input` 内の最初の一致を返します。一致しない 場合"
"は `nil` を返します。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:76
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:76"
msgid "`input` (string, required): The input text."
msgstr "`input` (string, 必須): 入力テキスト。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:78
msgid "Parameter notes:"
msgstr "パラメータに関する注意:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:80
msgid "`init` is a 1-based start position and defaults to `1`."
msgstr "`init` は 1 始まりの開始位置で、デフォルトは `1` です。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:81
msgid "`limit` must be greater than `0`."
msgstr "`limit` は `0` より大きくなければなりません。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:83
msgid "Return structures:"
msgstr "戻り値の構造:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:85
msgid "`Match`:"
msgstr "`Match`:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:85
msgid "`start` (integer): The 1-based start index."
msgstr "`start` (integer): 1 始まりの開始インデックス。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:85
msgid "`finish` (integer): The end index, directly usable with `string.sub`."
msgstr "`finish` (integer): `string.sub` にそのまま渡せる終了インデックス。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:85
msgid "`text` (string): The matched text."
msgstr "`text` (string): 一致したテキスト。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:89
msgid "`Captures`:"
msgstr "`Captures`:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:89
msgid "`full` (string): The full matched text."
msgstr "`full` (string): 完全一致したテキスト。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:89
msgid ""
"`groups` (table): An array of capture groups in capture order. Unmatched "
"groups are `nil`."
msgstr "`groups` (table): キャプチャ順のキャプチャグループ配列。一致しない グループは"
" `nil`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:89
msgid ""
"`named` (table): A mapping of named capture groups, keyed by group name."
msgstr "`named` (table): グループ名をキーにした名前付きキャプチャのマップ。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:95
msgid "find_all"
msgstr "find_all"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:97
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.re.Regex:find_all`."
msgstr "Canonical API name: `ptool.re.Regex:find_all`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:99
msgid "`re:find_all(input)` returns all matches in `input` as a `Match[]`."
msgstr "`re:find_all(input)` は `input` 内のすべての一致を `Match[]` として返します。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:101
msgid "captures"
msgstr "captures"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:103
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.re.Regex:captures`."
msgstr "Canonical API name: `ptool.re.Regex:captures`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:105
msgid ""
"`re:captures(input)` returns the first capture set in `input`, or `nil`."
msgstr ""
"`re:captures(input)` は `input` 内の最初のキャプチャセットを返します。 一致し"
"ない場合は `nil` を返します。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:107
msgid "captures_all"
msgstr "captures_all"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:109
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.re.Regex:captures_all`."
msgstr "Canonical API name: `ptool.re.Regex:captures_all`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:111
msgid ""
"`re:captures_all(input)` returns all capture sets in `input` as a "
"`Captures[]`."
msgstr ""
"`re:captures_all(input)` は `input` 内のすべてのキャプチャセットを "
"`Captures[]` として返します。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:113
msgid "replace"
msgstr "replace"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:115
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.re.Regex:replace`."
msgstr "Canonical API name: `ptool.re.Regex:replace`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:117
msgid "`re:replace(input, replacement)` replaces the first match in `input`."
msgstr "`re:replace(input, replacement)` は `input` 内の最初の一致を置換します。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:119
msgid "replace_all"
msgstr "replace_all"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:121
msgid "Canonical API name: `ptool.re.Regex:replace_all`."
msgstr "Canonical API name: `ptool.re.Regex:replace_all`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/re.md:123
msgid "`re:replace_all(input, replacement)` replaces all matches in `input`."
msgstr "`re:replace_all(input, replacement)` は `input` 内のすべての一致を 置換します"
